'''''475: Break the Silence,''''', (Umutwe wumwimerere: ''475: Trenquem el Silenci'' ) ni Sinema yo muri Maroc yo muri 2013 yerekana filime ngufi iyobowe na Hind Bensari .   Iyi filime yibanze ku buzima bwa Amina Fillali, umukobwa w’imyaka 16 ukomoka mu mujyi muto muri [[Maroc]]. Yiyahuye afata uburozi bwimbeba amaze gushyingiranwa numugabo wamusambanyije.   Yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya filime ryita ku burenganzira bwa muntu mu 2014. 

Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.  Yagize uruhare mu myigaragambyo muri [[Maroc]] gushyiraho itegeko rishya ryemerera abagabo baregwa gufata ku ngufu gushyingiranwa n’abo bahohotewe. Iyi filime yamamaye cyane mu kinyamakuru New York Times no mu muyoboro wa ARD wo mu [[Budage]] ndetse no kuri interineti.  yemeje kandi abayireba kuri TV 2M muri [[Maroc]] kandi isakaza mu bindi bihugu birimo [[Danimarike|Danemark]], [[Porutugali]], [[Kanada]] kandi igurishwa ku miyoboro irenga 20 ku isi.
